data.description: Welcome to your new oasis. Seated on 6.51 acres, this hobby farm has it all. Want to own cows or horses? Chickens or sheep? Whatever your heart desires. Fencing and gates are already placed and ready for animals. Beautiful trees surround the property providing lots of great shade.  Inside you will find custom oak cabinets, high quality Pella windows, and in-floor heating in the kitchen and bathroom. Two non-conforming bedrooms in the basement have closets and are ready for egress windows. This property has it all. Set up a showing today! 2023-10-15
